data.description: ESCAPE TO A WORLD OF WHOLESOME MEMORIES!Nestled among the tranquil embrace of nature, where the whispering trees meet the majestic mountains, your dream awaits. Welcome to the perfect family retreat - a 4-bedroom, 2,432 sq. foot mountain home, harmoniously perched on 3.56 acres of wooded bliss.Immerse yourself in breathtaking views of nearby mountains, where each sunrise and sunset paints the sky with colors that evoke a sense of wonder and serenity.Your Mountain Sanctuary Awaits:  4 spacious bedrooms that invite restful slumber.  A generous family room where future memories are waiting to be made.  An inviting eat-in kitchen, where laughter and memories are shared over homemade meals.  An elegant formal dining room, perfect for special occasions with loved ones.
